lyrics:
[Verse]
As the night unfolds, lost in time
I'm searching for the words to heal your mind
Through the raging storms, I'll find my way
To guide you back to where our hearts will stay

[Chorus]
Return to me, where love's melody resounds
Whispered on the winds, our souls forever bound
Through the darkest nights, we'll light the way
Hold my hand, let's embrace a brand-new day
